---
import '../styles/global.css'
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<html lang="fr" class="dark">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Minuit.strs - Programmes de cinéma à Strasbourg</title>
        <meta name="description" content="Minuit.strs - Tous les programmes de cinéma de Strasbourg en un seul endroit. Vox, UGC, Cosmos, Star et Star Saint-Exupéry.">
        <meta name="keywords" content="cinéma, Strasbourg, programmes, films, Vox, UGC, Cosmos, Star, Star Saint-Exupéry">
        <meta name="author" content="WyliGr">
        <meta property="og:title" content="Minuit.strs - Programmes de cinéma à Strasbourg">
        <meta property="og:description" content="Tous les programmes de cinéma de Strasbourg en un seul endroit. Vox, UGC, Cosmos, Star et Star Saint-Exupéry.">
        <meta property="og:type" content="website">
        <meta property="og:url" content="https://cinema.wyliam.fr">
        <meta property="og:image" content="https://cinema.wyliam.fr/favicon.ico">
        <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
        <meta name="twitter:title" content="Minuit.strs - Programmes de cinéma à Strasbourg">
        <meta name="twitter:description" content="Tous les programmes de cinéma de Strasbourg en un seul endroit. Vox, UGC, Cosmos, Star et Star Saint-Exupéry.">
        <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://cinema.wyliam.fr/favicon.ico">
        <link rel="canonical" href="https://cinema.wyliam.fr">
        <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico">
        <style>
            @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');
            @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:ital,wght@0,100..800;1,100..800&display=swap');
        
        body { font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; }
        .hide-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
        .hide-scroll { -ms-overflow-style: none; scrollbar-width: none; }
        
        .seance-badge.is-past {
            background-color: transparent !important;
            border-color: #171717 !important;
            color: #404040 !important;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .seance-badge.is-past .time-text {
            text-decoration: line-through;
        }
        .seance-badge.is-past .vost-tag {
            display: none !important;
        }
    </style>
</head>
 <body class="bg-[#0a0a09] text-white min-h-screen selection:bg-neutral-800 selection:text-white antialiased">
     <div class="navbar flex flex-row justify-between items-center mt-10 sm:mt-5 border-neutral-800/60 border-b py-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
            <a href="/">Minuit.strs</a>
        </h1>
        <ul class="hidden md:flex flex-row gap-6 mt-2 md:mt-0">
            <li><a href="#Home" class="text-white hover:text-gray-300">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#About" class="text-white hover:text-gray-300">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="#Theaters" class="text-white hover:text-gray-300">Theaters</a></li>
            <li><a href="#Support" class="text-white hover:text-gray-300">Support</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>

     <div class="#Home Hero text-center mt-20 pb-15 border-neutral-800/60 border-b max-w-6xl mx-auto w-full px-4 sm:px-6 py-8d">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">
            Stop making theaters<br>
            schedules a <i class="text-gray-400">painful</i> data
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-1xl mt-4">
            Every movie schedule, form every theater in Strasbourg, all in one place.
        </p>
        <div class="relative inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-4 group mt-12">
            <div
                class="absolute inset-0 duration-1000 opacity-60 transitiona-all bg-linear-to-r from-slate-700 to-slate-900 rounded-xl blur-lg filter group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:duration-200">
            </div>
            <a
                role="button"
                class="group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center text-base rounded-xl bg-slate-200 px-8 py-3 font-semibold text-black transition-all duration-100 hover:bg-slate-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-gray-600/30"
                title="payment"
                href="/dashboard">
                Look at the schedules
                <svg
                    aria-hidden="true"
                    viewBox="0 0 10 10"
                    height="10"
                    width="10"
                    fill="none"
                    class="mt-0.5 ml-2 -mr-1 stroke-black stroke-2">
                    <path d="M0 5h7" class="transition opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100"></path>
                    <path d="M1 1l4 4-4 4" class="transition group-hover:translate-x-[3px]"></path>
                </svg>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="About" class="mt-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="bg-neutral-900/50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-neutral-800">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-3xl">🎥</span>
                About the Project
            </h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
                Minuit.strs is a passion project designed to simplify the way you look at movie schedules in Strasbourg.
                With multiple theaters scattered across the city, keeping track of showtimes can be overwhelming.
                This platform aggregates all movie schedules from every theater in Strasbourg into one intuitive dashboard,
                making it easier than ever to plan your next cinema visit.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="Theaters" class="mt-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="bg-neutral-900/50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-neutral-800">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-3xl">🎬</span>
                Theaters Supported by the Dashboard
            </h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed mb-8">
                We currently support the following theaters in Strasbourg:
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div class="bg-neutral-800/50 rounded-lg p-4 border border-neutral-700 flex items-center justify-between">
                    <span class="text-neutral-300">Le Vox</span>
                    <a
                        href="https://www.cine-vox.com"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="text-white hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            width="20"
                            height="20"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/>
                            <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/>
                            <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/>
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-neutral-800/50 rounded-lg p-4 border border-neutral-700 flex items-center justify-between">
                    <span class="text-neutral-300">UGC Ciné Cité Strasbourg</span>
                    <a
                        href="https://www.ugc.fr/cinema.html?id=30"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="text-white hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            width="20"
                            height="20"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/>
                            <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/>
                            <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/>
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-neutral-800/50 rounded-lg p-4 border border-neutral-700 flex items-center justify-between">
                    <span class="text-neutral-300">Le Cosmos</span>
                    <a
                        href="https://www.cinema-cosmos.eu"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="text-white hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            width="20"
                            height="20"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/>
                            <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/>
                            <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/>
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-neutral-800/50 rounded-lg p-4 border border-neutral-700 flex items-center justify-between">
                    <span class="text-neutral-300">Le Star</span>
                    <a
                        href="https://www.cinema-star.com"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="text-white hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            width="20"
                            height="20"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/>
                            <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/>
                            <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/>
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-neutral-800/50 rounded-lg p-4 border border-neutral-700 flex items-center justify-between md:col-span-2">
                    <span class="text-neutral-300">Le Star Saint-Exupéry</span>
                    <a
                        href="https://www.cinema-star.com/saint-exupery"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="text-white hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            width="20"
                            height="20"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round">
                            <path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/>
                            <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/>
                            <line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/>
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="Support" class="mt-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="bg-neutral-900/50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-neutral-800">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-3xl">🎞️</span>
                Why Supporting Cinema
            </h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
                Cinema is more than just entertainment; it's a cultural experience that brings people together. Nowadays, however, the cinema is in danger. With an increasing number of movies being released exclusively on streaming platforms, this industry might one day disappear. That's why it's crucial to support local theaters by watching movies on the big screen whenever you can. I know it can be expensive, but trust me, it's money well spent. 
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
 <footer class="mt-16 py-8 border-t border-neutral-800/60 text-center text-neutral-500 text-sm max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
            <span>© 2026 Minuit.strs - Strasbourg Theater Movie Parser</span>
            <a
                href="https://github.com/WyliGr/Minuit-strs"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="flex items-center gap-2 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path
                        d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Star on GitHub</span>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-2">
            <span>Made with 🖤 by Wyligr</span>
        </div>
    </footer>
</html>